</para>
<variablelist>
<varlistentry><term><emphasis role="bold">Arguments:</emphasis></term>
<listitem><para>See <link linkend="mthAddEntryLine">AddEntryLine</link> for a description of the arguments.
</para></listitem></varlistentry>
